## 7️⃣ Performance Monitoring

### Core Web Vitals Targets

**Целевые метрики:**
- **LCP** (Largest Contentful Paint): **< 2.5s**
- **FID** (First Input Delay): **< 100ms**
- **CLS** (Cumulative Layout Shift): **< 0.1**
- **TTFB** (Time to First Byte): **< 600ms**

### Инструменты мониторинга

**Lighthouse CI в GitHub Actions:**

```yaml
# .github/workflows/lighthouse.yml
name: Lighthouse CI
on: [pull_request]
jobs:
  lighthouse:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - uses: treosh/lighthouse-ci-action@v9
        with:
          urls: |
            https://preview.unident.com
            https://preview.unident.com/doctors
          uploadArtifacts: true
```

**Vercel Analytics:**

```typescript
// app/layout.tsx
import { Analytics } from '@vercel/analytics/react';

export default function RootLayout({ children }: Props) {
  return (
    <html>
      <body>
        {children}
        <Analytics />
      </body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

**Real User Monitoring (RUM):**

```typescript
// app/components/web-vitals.tsx
'use client'
import { useReportWebVitals } from 'next/web-vitals';

export function WebVitals() {
  useReportWebVitals((metric) => {
    // Отправить в аналитику
    console.log(metric);
  });
}
```

### Performance Budget

**Жесткие лимиты:**
- **JavaScript bundle:**
  - Main bundle: **< 200KB** (gzipped)
  - Page bundle: **< 50KB** (gzipped)
- **Initial load:** **< 3s на 3G**
- **Images:** WebP/AVIF, **< 200KB** per image
- **CSS:** **< 50KB** (включая Tailwind)

**Автоматическая проверка:**

```json
// package.json
{
  "scripts": {
    "analyze": "ANALYZE=true next build",
    "check-bundle": "npm run analyze && bundlesize"
  },
  "bundlesize": [
    {
      "path": ".next/static/chunks/*.js",
      "maxSize": "200 kB"
    }
  ]
}
```

